    "tha-ap401:0.1_0": "The senior monks, Householders,",
    "tha-ap401:0.2_0": "With Pilindavaccha",
    "tha-ap401:0.3_0": "this is the most senior monk deserving of criticism.",
    "tha-ap401:1.1_0": "“The oceans and free of delusion,",
    "tha-ap401:1.2_0": "and the net of my flowers.",
    "tha-ap401:1.3_0": "the lotus ponds",
    "tha-ap401:1.4_0": "like a wheel-turning monarch.",
    "tha-ap401:10.1_0": "after which Dhamma he gave me a teaching,",
    "tha-ap401:10.2_0": "took me away from a great sage.",
    "tha-ap401:10.3_0": "Awakened One",
    "tha-ap401:10.4_0": "I became angry.",
    "tha-ap401:11.1_0": "I summoned them.",
    "tha-ap401:11.2_0": "‘You’ve accumulated a dispensation,",
    "tha-ap401:11.3_0": "The Buddha taught the Dhamma",
    "tha-ap401:11.4_0": "‘My life will come to an end.",
    "tha-ap401:12.1_0": "I’m fortunate, so very fortunate,",
    "tha-ap401:12.2_0": "and those who stay in your guest house.",
    "tha-ap401:12.3_0": "I too want to listen to the teaching",
    "tha-ap401:12.4_0": "we’ll worship the Teacher.’",
    "tha-ap401:13.1_0": "Whoever is not make amends for,",
