    "tha-ap401:25.4_0": "are the fruitless result",
    "tha-ap401:26.1_0": "My defilements have been burnt away by practicing absorption—",
    "tha-ap401:26.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "tha-ap401:26.3_0": "and live without defilements.",
    "tha-ap401:27.1_0": "It was truly for me",
    "tha-ap401:27.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "tha-ap401:27.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "tha-ap401:28.1_0": "Attaining the four kinds of textual analysis",
    "tha-ap401:28.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "tha-ap401:28.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "tha-ap401:29.1_0": "That is how these verses were recited by the senior venerable Sabbamitta.",
    "tha-ap401:3.1_0": "A stingy person,",
    "tha-ap401:3.2_0": "since his business is different,",
    "tha-ap401:3.3_0": "Peacocks and herons call out there,",
    "tha-ap401:3.4_0": "and the sweet cuckoos too.",
    "tha-ap401:30.1_0": "The ninth senior, the junior senior monks, and the ninth fine.",
    "tha-ap401:4.1_0": "the far shore, and the birds using,",
    "tha-ap401:4.2_0": "like a wheel-turning monarch,",
    "tha-ap401:4.3_0": "given to one who was something else,",
    "tha-ap401:4.4_0": "living at Campā,",
    "tha-ap401:5.1_0": "Why then, because I was such an arched harp,",
    "tha-ap401:5.2_0": "let alone the sal trees,",
    "tha-ap401:5.3_0": "Endowed with the seven gems,",
    "tha-ap401:5.4_0": "with jeweled earrings.",
    "tha-ap401:6.1_0": "Going to the tree,",
    "tha-ap401:6.2_0": "ties with different colors,",
    "tha-ap401:6.3_0": "they all day and night,",
    "tha-ap401:6.4_0": "leading to all the world.",
    "tha-ap401:7.1_0": "sixty hundreds of thousands,",
    "tha-ap401:7.2_0": "this hell is what they take up.",
    "tha-ap401:7.3_0": "Great women who live fortune,",
    "tha-ap401:7.4_0": "they consult the wise.",
    "tha-ap401:8.1_0": "I went forth,",
    "tha-ap401:8.2_0": "excellence of the world,",
    "tha-ap401:8.3_0": "confident and settled,",
    "tha-ap401:8.4_0": "I paid homage to the great crowd.",
    "tha-ap401:9.1_0": "Awakened One",
    "tha-ap401:9.2_0": "I lose my mind.",
    "tha-ap401:9.3_0": "The wise consented in silence,",
    "tha-ap401:9.4_0": "dig up the world."
